data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this stunning 5-bedroom, 2-bathroom home spanning over 2800 square feet. Nestled in a serene and quiet neighborhood, this property offers a tranquil retreat while being just a short stroll away from schools. The expansive open layout is perfect for both family gatherings and entertaining guests. With its large windows, the living area is bathed in natural light, creating an inviting ambiance throughout. The modern kitchen boasts ample counter space, making meal preparation a breeze. Storage will never be a concern, as this home offers an abundance of space to keep your belongings organized and easily accessible. Step outside to the fully fenced yard, where you can savor outdoor activities in complete privacy.  The property's prime location places it within walking distance to schools, making morning routines a breeze Whether you're looking for a peaceful retreat or a convenient home, this property offers it all.
